  "description": "Adds background music to the Overworld, Nether, and End. Custom tracks enhance the atmosphere of each dimension for a more immersive and intense gameplay experience in the Pingaland modpack.",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6JgPTWsz/Pingaland-Music-Curseforge-Icon.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"100\"><div style=\"border:3px solid #ff0000;text-align:center;color:#fff;font-size:1.5em;font-weight:bold\"><p><span style=\"color:#f00;font-size:1.7em\"><strong>Pingaland Music</strong></span><br><strong>is a custom mod for the </strong><span style=\"color:#f00\"><strong>Pingaland modpack</strong></span> <strong>that adds ambiance background music to Minecraft's</strong> <strong>three main dimensions</strong>.</p><p><strong>The goal of the mod is to enhance the gameplay experience with musical themes that match each dimension's environment, creating a more</strong> <strong>immersive, energetic, and distinctive atmosphere</strong>.</p></div><p><br></p><div style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/4gytaRTKuc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bBpJOKO.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"> </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_d_4.v_1_d_/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YHadOI4.png\" alt=\"Instagram\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"> </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"http://twitch.tv/p1as0p\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/URFEihO.png\" alt=\"Twitch\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></a></div><p><br><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/pingaland\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RVaO5gj.png\" alt=\"Play Pingaland\" width=\"1280\" height=\"507\"></a></p></div>",
